Plan: Dynamic Library Symbol Extraction (Replace libraryRegistry.ts)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       │
Context                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       │
Currently libraryRegistry.ts hardcodes FB signatures for Tc2_Standard, Tc2_System, Tc2_MC2 and Tc2_Utilities. This is unmaintainable and misses every user-installed library (mobject-core, etc.). The workspace already scans _Libraries/ for type names; this plan extends that to full signatures   │
(inputs, outputs, return types) for source libraries, and name-only for compiled libraries. Once complete, libraryRegistry.ts is no longer the source-of-truth for identifier/type resolution — the library files are.                                                                                 │
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       │
